<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f5f7; font-family: -apple-system, "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif }
    table { border-collapse: collapse }
    img { border: 0; line-height: 100%; outline: none; text-decoration: none }
    a { color: #1e40af }
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .wrapper { width: 100% !important; padding: 16px !important }
      .content-table { width: 100% !important }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f5f7">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
  <tr>
    <td align="center" style="padding:32px 16px">

      <table class="content-table" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation"
             style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08)">

        <!-- Header brand -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1e3a8a;padding:24px 40px">
            <span style="color:#ffffff;font-size:20px;font-weight:700">{{ brand_name }}</span>
            <div style="color:#93c5fd;font-size:12px;margin-top:2px;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase">
              {{ operator_profile }}
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Corpo -->
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:40px 40px 32px">

            <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:16px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6">
              Buongiorno,
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:16px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6">
              mi chiamo {{ brand_name }} e rappresento <strong>{{ operator_profile }}</strong>.
              Ho selezionato <strong>{{ company_name }}</strong> di {{ city }} perché ritengo di potervi
              offrire condizioni particolarmente vantaggiose.
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 28px;font-size:16px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6">
              Ci tenevo a contattarvi direttamente per presentare la nostra proposta in modo personalizzato.
            </p>

            <!-- Box proposta -->
            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
                   style="background:#eff6ff;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:28px">
              <tr>
                <td style="padding:24px 28px">
                  <div style="font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:#1e40af;margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:600">
                    La nostra proposta per {{ company_name }}
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#111827;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:12px">
                    {{ headline }}
                  </div>
                  <div style="font-size:14px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6">
                    {{ about_excerpt }}...
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>

            <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#111827">
              Perché vi contatto?
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0 0 28px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.7">
              Opero nella zona di <strong>{{ city }}</strong> e ho identificato la vostra attività come
              potenziale partner ideale. Sarei lieto di concordare una breve chiamata o visita
              per illustrarvi la proposta nel dettaglio — senza alcun impegno.
            </p>

            <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;margin:0 0 28px">

            <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-size:15px;color:#374151">Cordiali saluti,</p>
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#111827">{{ brand_name }}</p>
            <p style="margin:4px 0 0;font-size:14px;color:#6b7280">
              <a href="mailto:{{ brand_email }}" style="color:#1e40af">{{ brand_email }}</a>
            </p>

          </td>
        </tr>

        <!-- Footer GDPR -->
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#f9fafb;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:20px 40px;text-align:center">
            <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af;line-height:1.6">
              Hai ricevuto questa email perché {{ company_name }} è attiva a {{ city }}.
              I dati sono raccolti da fonti pubbliche (Google Maps, Pagine Gialle).
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#9ca3af">
              Non vuoi più ricevere comunicazioni?
              <a href="{{ optout_url }}" style="color:#6b7280;text-decoration:underline">
                Clicca qui per disiscriverti (opt-out GDPR)
              </a>
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>

      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<img src="{{ open_pixel_url }}" width="1" height="1" style="display:none;line-height:1px;font-size:1px" alt="">

</body>
</html>
